Write a java program to take name and year of birth as input from the keyboard and greet the person with his name printed
along with greeting message.You should also print the age of the person after greeting.
Note1:
Greeting is a task.so we keep the task in a separate method and let the method be of "type 3" i.e method which would 
accept the parameter and would not return the value
Note2:
Calculating age is also a task hence keep it in a separate method of "type 4" i.e which would accept the parameter and
would return a value.
Sample Input:
Omkar
2020
Sample Output:
Hello Omkar
You are 3 years old